        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<div class="example wow animate__bounceInUp">我是内容<p>Vauable</p><h2 id="前言"><a href="#前言" class="headerlink" title="前言"></a>前言</h2><h3 id="本人专业所学为“概率论与数理统计”，以下为本人在学习过程中点点滴滴搜刮的宝藏，欢迎大家来取材"><a href="#本人专业所学为“概率论与数理统计”，以下为本人在学习过程中点点滴滴搜刮的宝藏，欢迎大家来取材" class="headerlink" title="本人专业所学为“概率论与数理统计”，以下为本人在学习过程中点点滴滴搜刮的宝藏，欢迎大家来取材"></a>本人专业所学为“概率论与数理统计”，以下为本人在学习过程中点点滴滴搜刮的宝藏，欢迎大家来取材</h3><h3 id="下方多图警告"><a href="#下方多图警告" class="headerlink" title="下方多图警告"></a>下方多图警告</h3><h3 id="1-随机事件机器概率"><a href="#1-随机事件机器概率" class="headerlink" title="1.随机事件机器概率"></a>1.随机事件机器概率</h3><p><img src="https://pica.zhimg.com/80/v2-cc140f71c782dc3ea96ddfb6d22c665d_720w.jpg?source=3af55fa1"></p><p><img src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-4a0b82b407465521ed8a9445588ca491_720w.jpg?source=3af55fa1"></p><p><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-74f90038f54f1a3e33bd352650bde2f6_720w.jpg?source=3af55fa1"></p><h3 id="2-随机变量及其分布"><a href="#2-随机变量及其分布" class="headerlink" title="2.随机变量及其分布"></a>2.随机变量及其分布</h3><p><img src="https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-59d4d22cbf903afc06d8167e2bb6c1e2_720w.jpg?source=3af55fa1"></p><p><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-9fe6a0e9ad1e6ed44ffc96b082b9bfb5_720w.jpg?source=3af55fa1"></p><p><img src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-6980a0701f917c18e190c227f52a7f61_720w.jpg?source=3af55fa1"></p><p><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-dae7ee66ee9e0da05fe283b569d7eb58_720w.jpg?source=3af55fa1"></p><h2 id="3-二维随机变量及其分布"><a href="#3-二维随机变量及其分布" class="headerlink" title="3.二维随机变量及其分布"></a>3.二维随机变量及其分布</h2><p><img src="https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-d1f1070a0378d55b55e4d014edb7b2e4_720w.jpg?source=3af55fa1"></p><p><img src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-42292ccb21a4926ffcb8331e1868bb60_720w.jpg?source=3af55fa1"></p><p><img src="https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-f845daa016ff387c00164ae7672d8390_720w.jpg?source=3af55fa1"></p><p><img src="https://pica.zhimg.com/80/v2-d682804eaea8632c8be35e67af726fca_720w.jpg?source=3af55fa1"></p><p><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c7fc53837c85167ccba0864c0644b313_720w.jpg?source=3af55fa1"></p><h2 id="4-随机变量的数字特征"><a href="#4-随机变量的数字特征" class="headerlink" title="4.随机变量的数字特征"></a>4.随机变量的数字特征</h2><p><img src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-01b10e185b35e0b051bf69815c5617f0_720w.jpg?source=3af55fa1"></p><p><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-013194cc9179662ec437db4bf5386023_720w.jpg?source=3af55fa1"></p><p><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-013194cc9179662ec437db4bf5386023_720w.jpg?source=3af55fa1"></p><p><img src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-516bca97dc0689003ef8ce067daca753_720w.jpg?source=3af55fa1"></p><p><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-f5c1edd6e1520340050397a536b10690_720w.jpg?source=3af55fa1"></p><h2 id="5-大数定律和中心极限极限定理"><a href="#5-大数定律和中心极限极限定理" class="headerlink" title="5.大数定律和中心极限极限定理"></a>5.大数定律和中心极限极限定理</h2><p><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-4ca2c25cd38dadcd6a32b2ff000fba38_720w.jpg?source=3af55fa1"></p><h2 id="6-样本及抽样分布"><a href="#6-样本及抽样分布" class="headerlink" title="6.样本及抽样分布"></a>6.样本及抽样分布</h2><p><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-85d41e8541be6e414d7ca9a2f3d6136f_720w.jpg?source=3af55fa1"></p><p><img src="https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-b873fc9bef08eda9597f493ebbc97a0e_720w.jpg?source=3af55fa1"></p><p><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-139d6f5a818ff907ba05662a1f782f87_720w.jpg?source=3af55fa1"></p><h2 id="7-参数估计"><a href="#7-参数估计" class="headerlink" title="7.参数估计"></a>7.参数估计</h2><p><img src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-708b8336156db00bbdf03b0e11e79e5c_720w.jpg?source=3af55fa1"></p><p><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-44df08300743b88594d9ba7c05e3f185_720w.jpg?source=3af55fa1"></p><p><img src="https://pica.zhimg.com/80/v2-8479d580eadbc57a70e30a72d82ac3b6_720w.jpg?source=3af55fa1"></p><h2 id="8-假设检验"><a href="#8-假设检验" class="headerlink" title="8.假设检验"></a>8.假设检验</h2><p><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-e07f6bc3bf268de55db1b482dabe75b8_720w.jpg?source=3af55fa1"></p><p><img src="https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-6e080f342c41352fd1ced1b0e90930c5_720w.jpg?source=3af55fa1"></p><p><img src="https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-667464ff3ea98e222d97bfce47b1a552_720w.jpg?source=3af55fa1"></p><h2 id="9-随机过程"><a href="#9-随机过程" class="headerlink" title="9.随机过程"></a>9.随机过程</h2><p><img src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-f9bf374fb2652aad07c11130beabf02b_720w.jpg?source=3af55fa1"></p><p><img src="https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-4826f498b170155c96dea3b4dea266f7_720w.jpg?source=3af55fa1"></p><p><img src="https://pica.zhimg.com/80/v2-02de82b03c7eb6538e75efa19e48984c_720w.jpg?source=3af55fa1"></p><h2 id="10-马尔可夫链"><a href="#10-马尔可夫链" class="headerlink" title="10.马尔可夫链"></a>10.马尔可夫链</h2><p><img src="https://pica.zhimg.com/80/v2-f72d135e4041cf8bccb3c8ec7055a036_720w.jpg?source=3af55fa1"></p><p><img src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-4227a07541843a41651b86be952c02cf_720w.jpg?source=3af55fa1"></p><h2 id="课业繁忙，不一定会及时回复问题和建议，还请见谅哦～🎉"><a href="#课业繁忙，不一定会及时回复问题和建议，还请见谅哦～🎉" class="headerlink" title="课业繁忙，不一定会及时回复问题和建议，还请见谅哦～🎉"></a>课业繁忙，不一定会及时回复问题和建议，还请见谅哦～🎉</h2></div>]]></content>
      
      
      
